Package: RichCluster
Type: Package
Title: Fast, Robust Clustering Algorithms for Gene Enrichment Data
Version: 1.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Date: 2025-06-02
Authors@R: person("Sarah", "Hong", role =
     c("aut", "cre"), email =
     "ssh2198@columbia.edu")
Description: RichCluster is a fast C++ agglomerative hierarchical clustering algorithm packaged 
    into easily callable R functions, designed to help cluster biological 'terms' based on how similar 
    of genes are expressed in their activation.
